=======NOTES======

input colors: 
dafault:    background-color: rgb(149, 149, 149, 0.7);
hover:      background-color: rgb(149, 149, 149, 0.8);
focus:      background-color: rgb(149, 149, 149, 0.9);
active:     background-color: rgb(149, 149, 149, 0.7);

NOTE: if user changes his phone number and login email, this value is still remembered in item which was created in past

update vagrant box:
    vagrant box update

update npm:
    npm install -g npm

require package for API based email drivers
composer require guzzlehttp/guzzle

requieres to use AWS s3 storage
composer require league/flysystem-aws-s3-v3

php artisan storage:link
The [/home/vagrant/code/rigmanager/public/storage] link has been connected to [/home/vagrant/code/rigmanager/storage/app/public].

